OL,7,FSeven others were critically injured
OL,8,Fand a total of 18 people remain in
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FThe flight was diverted to Bangkok's
OL,12,FSuvarnabhumi Airport after the
OL,13,Fincident where people are receiving
OL,14,Fmedical treatment.
OL,16,FAt a press conference held after the
OL,17,Fplane landed, the general manager of
OL,18,Fthe airport said the man died from a
OL,19,Fpossible heart attack.
