OL,7,FThe statement went on: "Our priority
OL,8,Fis to provide all possible assistance
OL,9,Fto all passengers and crew on board
OL,10,Fthe aircraft.
OL,12,F"We are working with the local
OL,13,Fauthorities in Thailand to provide the
OL,14,Fnecessary medical assistance, and
OL,15,Fsending a team to Bangkok to provide
OL,16,Fany additional assistance needed."
